*kismet-ubertooth-2012.10.1-r1 (25 Apr 2013)

  25 Apr 2013; Rick Farina <zerochaos@gentoo.org>
  +kismet-ubertooth-2012.10.1-r1.ebuild, kismet-ubertooth-9999.ebuild:
  subslot dep on kismet to prevent incorrect plugin from crashing kismet (forces
  rebuild of plugin when kismet changes)

